rows.label: qst105408_msg0001
rows.name:
Did you come to see it too,
mo? The legendary treasure!

rows.label: qst105408_msg0002
rows.name:
This is the Catastrophe Puzzle,
mo! Amazing, mo! So cool, mo!

rows.label: qst105408_msg0003
rows.name:
The treasure of salvagers'
dreams has finally been
salvaged by Zubzub, mo!

rows.label: qst105408_msg0004
rows.name:
You had fill of staring? Then
Zubzub go to sell treasure
at Central Exchange now.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0005
rows.name:
Mo? You want the
Catastrophe Puzzle, mo?

rows.label: qst105408_msg0006
rows.name:
Zubzub was going to sell it
anyway... and it's actually
heavy to carry, so it's fine, mo.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0007
rows.name: Zubzub will sell it for 500,000G, mo.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0008
rows.name: That's not a surprising price, mo.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0009
rows.name:
Zubzub had to wait patiently
for the Divine Beasts to
align perfectly...

rows.label: qst105408_msg0010
rows.name:
...and then hauled it up
with expensive cylinders
and an amazing wire, mo.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0011
rows.name:
It's not worth it unless
Zubzub gets that much, mo.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0013
rows.name: Pay

rows.label: qst105408_msg0014
rows.name: Don't pay

rows.label: qst105408_msg0101
rows.name:
One, two, three... 500,000G,
Zubzub has received it all, mo!

rows.label: qst105408_msg0102
rows.name:
The Catastrophe Puzzle is yours,
mo. You can take it, mo.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0103
rows.name: It's super heavy, so be careful, mo.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0104
rows.name:
It would have cost about 5,000G
to carry it to the Central Exchange,
so this was a big help, mo.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0105
rows.name:
Well then, Zubzub will go back
to treasure hunting, mo! Thanks
for your business, mo~!

rows.label: qst105408_msg0201
rows.name:
If you don't pay, Zubzub
will just sell it, mo.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0202
rows.name:
...But Zubzub doesn't want to
carry it, so Zubzub will wait
for you to get the money, mo.

rows.label: qst105408_msg0301
rows.name:
If you want the Catastrophe
Puzzle, Zubzub will sell
it for 500,000G, mo.
